  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ee58327d271ecbba1ac14c7254587a5c.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't remember why and how you are stranded in Vanada. As you proceed to find answers to the question where you are, you get in contact with the sisters Aya and Chiyo. It quickly becomes clear that they need help. Your help. A dangerous journey awaits, where your main goal is to collect enough KADOS to be strong enough to fight and defeat AKZU. Do you have what it takes to help Aya and Chiyo to free Vanada from the dominion of AKZU?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/47bd62d54d81cd6f0adff18336fafc16.avif?t=1772300049\" width=573 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/d45a46921c3acbc937e77f33ef54df67.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KADO HUNTER is a 2D, pixel art and story based adventure rpg.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/b164a63dc8998ccd1a432f72a9060831.avif?t=1772300049\" width=800 height=272 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Action combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies in an action-combat fighting system, where you are gaining experience for leveling your character as well as collecting items and money. Within your adventure you will be learning new skills, find new weapons and increase your overall strength. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/30ece044797423fdf63fd9ece4a5b385.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=190 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/30ece044797423fdf63fd9ece4a5b385.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/30ece044797423fdf63fd9ece4a5b385.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>                                                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/9c24ab8c126bcfe6ce78fbd3738358a2.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=190 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/9c24ab8c126bcfe6ce78fbd3738358a2.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/9c24ab8c126bcfe6ce78fbd3738358a2.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80bd9e4e616c224e5f22931e14bcd9ee.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=196 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80bd9e4e616c224e5f22931e14bcd9ee.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80bd9e4e616c224e5f22931e14bcd9ee.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quests</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be lead through the game with quests and a built-in questlog. Beside the mainstory quests, you are also able to solve sidequests and missions which are granting you rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Activities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are several activities to explore, such as dungeons, world bosses, abysses and much more. <br>The new activity \"KADO MASTERS\" - a card fight game where you're able to compete against the people in Vanada has been newly added!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/2dc58aae89f88a7ae3d31bd76aa9c940.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=792 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/2dc58aae89f88a7ae3d31bd76aa9c940.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/2dc58aae89f88a7ae3d31bd76aa9c940.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KADOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 300+ KADOS which can be collected - every KADO is different and is hooked to a rarity system. You can rewatch every owned KADO in your Kado album! You can see a few examples below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ff93b8143442555b1084b7eac487e848.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=414 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ff93b8143442555b1084b7eac487e848.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ff93b8143442555b1084b7eac487e848.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80d5608c07a93a8ba6edba4090471950.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/96006c089534d412c2cd80e4d9aec90e.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/afe2232fc199cca4f151447e4e1a754a.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/b57a0f6a21cfd47313c04182485bb32a.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/10b128bd96cadd31a7f4861650d69ef3.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/bbaf71814cc979e2b04121c192d40f86.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/1fcf17922e0cbf9b4db9fc0599cbe63c.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/adf064a3f4d1d848af49a63e07bed217.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are an indie team of two cousins dreaming about creating games which we and you enjoy. We have been passionate gamers for as long as we can remember and of course at some point we asked ourselves whether we not only wanted to play games - but also create them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is our goal? As KADO HUNTER is our very first project, we gained a lot of skills, new experiences and learned a lot about developing and designing while working on it. We are fully aware that we have only just scratched the surface so far, but we won't stop here - quite the opposite. We have tons of ideas that we really want to bring to life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We from SaltyGames hope, that you're enjoying our work. Thanks for reading this and maybe playing our game. If you have any suggestions, feedback or anything else, feel free to join our Discord server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/097905a4288ac193705c6d546eeb67e9.avif?t=1772300049\" width=184 height=237 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ee58327d271ecbba1ac14c7254587a5c.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't remember why and how you are stranded in Vanada. As you proceed to find answers to the question where you are, you get in contact with the sisters Aya and Chiyo. It quickly becomes clear that they need help. Your help. A dangerous journey awaits, where your main goal is to collect enough KADOS to be strong enough to fight and defeat AKZU. Do you have what it takes to help Aya and Chiyo to free Vanada from the dominion of AKZU?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/47bd62d54d81cd6f0adff18336fafc16.avif?t=1772300049\" width=573 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/d45a46921c3acbc937e77f33ef54df67.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KADO HUNTER is a 2D, pixel art and story based adventure rpg.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/b164a63dc8998ccd1a432f72a9060831.avif?t=1772300049\" width=800 height=272 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Action combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies in an action-combat fighting system, where you are gaining experience for leveling your character as well as collecting items and money. Within your adventure you will be learning new skills, find new weapons and increase your overall strength. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/30ece044797423fdf63fd9ece4a5b385.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=190 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/30ece044797423fdf63fd9ece4a5b385.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/30ece044797423fdf63fd9ece4a5b385.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>                                                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/9c24ab8c126bcfe6ce78fbd3738358a2.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=190 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/9c24ab8c126bcfe6ce78fbd3738358a2.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/9c24ab8c126bcfe6ce78fbd3738358a2.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80bd9e4e616c224e5f22931e14bcd9ee.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=196 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80bd9e4e616c224e5f22931e14bcd9ee.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80bd9e4e616c224e5f22931e14bcd9ee.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quests</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be lead through the game with quests and a built-in questlog. Beside the mainstory quests, you are also able to solve sidequests and missions which are granting you rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Activities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are several activities to explore, such as dungeons, world bosses, abysses and much more. <br>The new activity \"KADO MASTERS\" - a card fight game where you're able to compete against the people in Vanada has been newly added!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/2dc58aae89f88a7ae3d31bd76aa9c940.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=792 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/2dc58aae89f88a7ae3d31bd76aa9c940.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/2dc58aae89f88a7ae3d31bd76aa9c940.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KADOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 300+ KADOS which can be collected - every KADO is different and is hooked to a rarity system. You can rewatch every owned KADO in your Kado album! You can see a few examples below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ff93b8143442555b1084b7eac487e848.poster.avif?t=1772300049\" width=414 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ff93b8143442555b1084b7eac487e848.webm?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/ff93b8143442555b1084b7eac487e848.mp4?t=1772300049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/80d5608c07a93a8ba6edba4090471950.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/96006c089534d412c2cd80e4d9aec90e.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/afe2232fc199cca4f151447e4e1a754a.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/b57a0f6a21cfd47313c04182485bb32a.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/10b128bd96cadd31a7f4861650d69ef3.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/bbaf71814cc979e2b04121c192d40f86.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/1fcf17922e0cbf9b4db9fc0599cbe63c.avif?t=1772300049\" width=222 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/adf064a3f4d1d848af49a63e07bed217.webp?t=1772300049\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are an indie team of two cousins dreaming about creating games which we and you enjoy. We have been passionate gamers for as long as we can remember and of course at some point we asked ourselves whether we not only wanted to play games - but also create them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is our goal? As KADO HUNTER is our very first project, we gained a lot of skills, new experiences and learned a lot about developing and designing while working on it. We are fully aware that we have only just scratched the surface so far, but we won't stop here - quite the opposite. We have tons of ideas that we really want to bring to life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We from SaltyGames hope, that you're enjoying our work. Thanks for reading this and maybe playing our game. If you have any suggestions, feedback or anything else, feel free to join our Discord server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981880/extras/097905a4288ac193705c6d546eeb67e9.avif?t=1772300049\" width=184 height=237 /></span></p>",
